Summary
	The Account Enquiry Batch Processing Module automates the processing of account enquiry transactions using the Spring batch framework. It reads eligible records from the ADHD table based on the instance number passed through VM arguments and marks then as in progress(ADHD_STATUS=25).The module invokes the EIS Account Enquiry API, processes the response, and validates parameters such as Error Code, Account System, Product ID, and Branch Number. Based on the validations results, the transaction status is updated as success(ADHD_STATUS=37) or failure(ADHD_STATUS=28).This Module ensures reliable and efficient batch execution through exception handling and fault tolerance.

